🛡️ 5. Key Takeaways

Defensive Layer: This case highlights the importance of monitoring network traffic for unauthorized GitHub or external script downloads.


Offensive Layer: Exposed API documentation (OpenAPI/Swagger) is a critical information disclosure that can lead to total system takeover.


Remediation: For the organization, I implemented stricter email filtering and blocked the identified C2 domains at the firewall level.
